welcome_message_body: Welcome to Onalaska, USA! Get ready to experience the charming small-town feel and explore our beautiful parks, vibrant community, and delicious local cuisine. We hope you have a wonderful stay and enjoy all that Onalaska has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Municipal Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal handles all freight and cargo shipments at Municipal Airport.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
